Class LibrarySpectrum

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.mpa.algorithms.similarity.LibrarySpectrum
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    RankedLibrarySpectrum

    public class LibrarySpectrum
extends Object
    Data structure for a library spectrum. Holds the MGF spectrum file, the peptide sequence and the protein annotation.
    Author:
    Thilo Muth, Alexander Behne
